data.description:
This is a unique opportunity for the perfect, move-in ready house!  Current owners have LOVED this house and made all the right upgrades. This listing is worth your time to schedule a showing! 

3 Bedrooms | Renovated bath | Bright kitchen with great upgrades (natural gas stove) | Large pantry & laundry room | Large living spaces | Superb bonus room | Good dining space | Well-kept backyard | Square footage!

Refrigerator included!
